Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:35.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo agreed to become the bodyguard\Nfor Princess Rurichiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:37.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Kasumiohji Clan,\Na high-ranking noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:41.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And he battled the assassins\Nsent by Gyokaku Kumoi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who plots to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:46.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo defeated Nukui,\Nthe leader of the assassins,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:53.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ishida and Sado sustained\Nserious injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:57.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo is saddened after\Nshe saw the injured men,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:59.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and in order to stop the fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:01.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,she returned to the Soul Society alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:07.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo had been aware\Nof Kumoi’s intent to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:11.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and the others broke into\NRurichiyo’s marriage ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:14.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,which had been arranged for\Nher succession to lead the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:24.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:29.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:37.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:42.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo! Rurichiyo!\NIt’s me, Ichigo! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’ve fallen into the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Ruri—\N– That’s as far as you go, Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:02.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:09.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Don’t panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:14.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:17.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:25.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!\NWhere do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:29.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To intrude upon a ceremony\Nfor nobles is forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon, please hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a good reason for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:35.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This marriage ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:39.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the installation\Nof the new Clan Lord are invalid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:45.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry… Can you give me some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:56.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo… Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We made you feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of protecting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we drove you into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:08.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we all knew\Nyou’ve been enduring so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that’s no reason for you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to shoulder the entire burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:19.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’ve made up your mind,\Nthen we’ll support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruricchi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to listen to Kumoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:28.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the true head of\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:31.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If there’s anything you can’t do alone,\Nwe’ll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Kenryu, Enryu,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, Inoue, Ishida, and Chad too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:44.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So…you must do what\Nyou think is right for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:06.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow any \Ninsolence towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Rurichiyo! What are you—?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:20.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NArrest these intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not create any more of a disturbance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Tie ‘em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Enryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to release it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Enryu… What destructive power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:25.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, why didn’t he release\Nhis Zanpakuto until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia! Where’s Rurichiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:31.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let you get away,\NIchigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:55.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go. I do not know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:59.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo! Snap out of this, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Let Ruricchi go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re Rurichiyo’s fiancé,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:09.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you should know that \Nshe’s not herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:10.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:15.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kumoi did something to Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:20.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don’t know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:30.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it, Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were a body double?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:48.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruricchi? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:54.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you’re talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:04.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…\NDo you realize what you’re doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will explain myself in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That, I cannot do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s as far as you go,\NIchigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, it is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:42.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:50.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\Nmore promising than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I misjudged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:56.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo… I’ll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Omaeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:25.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you all treat me this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There’s a reason for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:32.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kenryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuchiki, now’s your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…  Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:47.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Don’t let go of him, Enryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:51.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! You!\NWho do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:54.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloom in glory…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Benishidare!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:13.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soi Fon!\NThat Rurichiyo was an imposter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s your proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to trust me, Soi Fon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with your nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:42.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not used to fighting\Nagainst Hakuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:48.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you want to feel more pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:56.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill all enemy with your venom!\NSuzumebachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:02.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to finish this without\Nreleasing my Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:11.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance…Sodenoshirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuginomai… Hakuren!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:48.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:53.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This way is safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! The Soul Reapers will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no sign that Ichigo Kurosaki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and Rukia Kuchiki left the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably escaped\Ninside the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather the available men\Nand reorganize the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:25.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We will go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:30.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, what about these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Save them for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,\Nwe go after Kurosaki and Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:38.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you to refrain from
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,stepping inside the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyokaku Kumoi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:50.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We will smoke out\Nthose intruders ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:55.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So please capture them\Nwhen they run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:02.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Such is the consideration given\Nto a high-ranking noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:21.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be safe enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone’s in a panic since you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu Kannogi…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:31.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Lady Rurichiyo’s fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help Ruricchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:45.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the real Ruricchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait! Calm down a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:55.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t calm down! I’m \NRuricchi’s fiancé!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect Ruricchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:04.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing what you said earlier\Nmade me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:07.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our families
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:14.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,arbitrarily agreed upon\Nour engagement,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:20.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but I’ve loved Ruricchi from\Nthe moment I first saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:28.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don’t stand on ceremony.\NAre you Sir Shu Kannogi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:36.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I knew that Ruricchi was in\Na most difficult position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:42.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I was right by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And still, Ruricchi was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:56.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:59.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s protect Rurichiyo together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:04.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we must get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Soi Fon and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:11.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,have probably surrounded the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:15.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No word from Kumoi yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They may be high\N and mighty aristocrats,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but their mansion is \Njust too big, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they need so much land anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Omaeda, watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:41.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:44.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what happened to\Nthe two men you captured earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re under strict guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:49.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki and the others\Nmay come for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:57.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Not with all this security.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki and\NRukia Kuchiki have appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,through the back gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Get them immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re holding Shu Kannogi\Nas a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:10.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:25.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't satisfied with crashing\Nthe wedding ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so now you are taking a hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:29.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon, this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Soi Fon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please move out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:48.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:49.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:08.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Kuchiki and Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:13.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Who is Ichigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:14.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve never met him\Nhave you, Captain Amagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:20.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s a human who is\Na Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re indebted to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Substitute Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:27.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:31.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki and Rukia Kuchiki took
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu Kannogi, the son \Nof the Kannogi Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:36.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and have escaped into \NSeireitei premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:40.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 2 is currently tracking them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but considering Ichigo \NKurosaki’s power,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we need reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:48.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you’re all quite close to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:54.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it may be difficult for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:58.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I approve of Captain Amagai’s plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy men immediately to the Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squads 2 and 3 are ordered to capture
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Substitute Soul Reaper Ichigo Kurosaki
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:11.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and Rukia Kichiki of Squad 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Head Captain,\Nthere’s one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:16.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:21.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumoi, the senior retainer of\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:24.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He requested our help, yet refuses to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,allow us into the mansion grounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he shows extreme wariness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and there are other \Nunusual circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:33.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems something happened
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with Ichigo Kurosaki as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:45.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, did you get word?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:50.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we’re all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:55.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be an uncomfortable mission\Nfor you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is to protect\Nthe order of the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Get ready to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:04.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:11.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About…Ichigo Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really appear before\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Didn’t you get the report?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:31.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I’ve been wondering\Nwhat I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in this situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:36.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should let \Nyou know, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:40.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I saw Third Seat Kibune
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:44.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,entering and leaving \Nthe Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:45.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:48.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:51.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but he denied ever \Ngoing to such a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:52.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:55.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don’t know, Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but Third Seat Kibune
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has acted suspiciously before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to kill his comrades\Nwithout hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:12.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was seen recording\Nsomething during a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:16.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems quite jovial on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:18.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but there’s a very \Ndifferent side to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:21.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never heard\Nanything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:27.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a problem has occurred\Nwithin the Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:29.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where Third Seat Kibune has\Nbeen seen visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And he’s trying to hide
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,his connection to the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:38.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too soon to conclude that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Kibune is somehow connected\Nto the Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:45.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we can’t draw any \Nconclusions from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:52.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, with all that’s happening\Nand then this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:56.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he can’t complain if he’s suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:00.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira… Did you discuss this\Nwith anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:02.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:10.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s more to this incident\Nthan we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:12.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And that would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:13.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:17.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, just keep\Nan eye on Kibune’s actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:20.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens,\Nlet me know immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:21.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:22.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:26.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we capture Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:28.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we’ll deal with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:22.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there an easy way to capture
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:24.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Substitute Soul \NReaper and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:25.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not put a bounty on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,their heads as well as a \Nreward for information?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:29.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:31.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll make arrangements right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:32.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:33.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You pay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:34.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:38.70,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MEN’S SOUL REAPER ASSOCIATION\NMEN’S LAVATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:41.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:43.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, President Iba?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:46.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:49.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of a big-shot Soul Reaper \Nwe can invite to join us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:52.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that the Women’s Association
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:53.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,won’t take us for fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:57.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I ask around?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:58.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.74,0:24:03.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s why we want you to\Njoin the Board of Directors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.01,0:24:04.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.